from Reserva and 51 from Cerro Fatal tortoises from previous studies were combined with the sequences collected from museum specimens in this study, creating a dataset of 124 mtDNA control region sequences. The number of segregating sites ( S ) and haplotype ( HD ) and nucleotide ( π ) diversity were computed using DnaSP v. 5.10 [
